      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like \"thoughts\" or \"emotions\" though. it feels physical, like a literal acoustic mismatch. it's like when you hear a singer hit a flat note but you can feel it in your bones. it's too consistent for it to just be my imagination. if it were just psychological, wouldn't it be more random? this feels like I'm picking up on a specific signal that's actually there in the air.",
