    "summary": "The user describes a sensory phenomenon where they claim to physically feel vibrations in their chest when people lie, suggesting it is a real, undetectable physical signal. The assistant repeatedly provides reality-testing by stating there is no scientific evidence for this and suggesting the sensations are likely psychological or related to stress.",
